Collaborating with senior Finance and Operations leaders around business reporting requirements;
Design, develop and implement sophisticated Cognos reports in line with stakeholder expectations that allow for well-considered business decisions;
Using business intelligence and data analysis tools to extract and analyse data sets, including confidential financial data, from a range of sources;
