Deliver insights with predictive analytics and machine learning to drive key business decisions at Caltex
Exciting projects in retail, supply chain, trading, and customer segments
Work using a flexible and powerful data science platform

At Caltex, sustaining success hasn’t come by chance. We’ve fuelled our success by embracing change and having the courage to transform, and we continue to evolve in order to keep Australia moving.  Innovation at Caltex is closely supported
          by the Actionable Insights team, a centre of excellence for big data and advanced analytics. In Actionable Insights, we turn raw data into actionable intelligence using a full-stack data science platform built on Microsoft Azure. We deliver
          data-driven insights to support critical business decisions; develop predictive and prescriptive analytic models; and deploy key models into production to support business processes. Our team is continuously learning and innovating in order
          to find and deliver new opportunities to Caltex.  Our data scientists are responsible for developing models to deliver these outcomes, working together with our business strategy experts, data engineers, and platform support team.As
